data.title: We Provide Plain Instructions for Victorious Living
data.meta_description: We Provide Plain Instructions for Victorious Living
data.text:
Are you new to the community?

Seed of Faith International is planting and putting down roots to reach the people in our neighborhood and the surrounding areas for Christ.

We are a place where everyone is welcome, encouraged, and supported as they seek after God’s will for their life. We intend to work locally to bring the Gospel of Jesus to our neighbors, making a lasting impact on our city as we serve and love our people in Jesus’ name.

By the grace of God, we look forward to growing as a church and seeing our community transformed by the power of Christ.
